A4.text: Habsburg Castle is a medieval Swiss fortress located in what is now Habsburg, Switzerland.

A5.text: Habsburg Castle remained property of the House of Habsburg until 1415, when Duke Frederick IV of Austria lost the canton of Aargau to the Swiss Confederacy.
